data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This spacious two-story residence spans 2000 square feet, offering ample room for comfortable living and entertaining. With four generously sized bedrooms and two full baths, this home provides the perfect blend of functionality and style. Nestled on a sprawling 0.75-acre lot, the property boasts a harmonious balance of indoor and outdoor living. The expansive yard offers limitless possibilities, from gardening to hosting gatherings under the open sky. Whether you're enjoying the modern amenities inside or the vast greenery outside, this home is a sanctuary for those seeking both space and tranquility.
